    <article class="prose"><p class="eyebrow">Portable edition</p><h1>下载</h1><p>网站正文与 PDF 由同一个固定提交的 Typst 权威源生成；网页负责阅读与导航，PDF 保留分页版本。</p>
      <div class="download-card" id="overview"><div><strong>Sevara 权威快照</strong><small>与公开规范网页同源；保留稳定的概览下载地址。</small></div><a class="button" href="/sevara/downloads/sevara-overview.pdf">PDF</a></div>
      <div class="download-card" id="companion"><div><strong>Sevara 完整资产伴读</strong><small>由权威仓的 explanatory Typst 源生成，不取代公开规范。</small></div><a class="button" href="/sevara/downloads/sevara-language-companion.pdf">PDF</a></div>
